en the bones) | Latin ([[wikt:bursa#Latin|bursa]]), purse; Ancient Greek [[wikt:βύρσα#Ancient Greek|βύρσα]] (''búrsa''), hide, wine-skin | [[Synovial bursa|Bursa]], [[bursitis]] |}
